videos.description: Charlie Brewer caps off a 10-play, 78-yard drive with a two-yard rushing touchdown to give Baylor an early lead over Oklahoma.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brewer scoots into end zone for Baylor TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brewer scoots into end zone for Baylor TD

videos.description: Charlie Brewer's 30-yard touchdown throw lands perfectly into the hands of Denzel Mims to extend Baylor's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brewer lofts beautiful TD ball to Mims) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brewer lofts beautiful TD ball to Mims

videos.description: Jalen Hurts tries eluding pressure, but drops the ball and it is recovered by Baylor's Terrel Bernard.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts coughs up fumble in Sooners territory) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts coughs up fumble in Sooners territory

videos.description: Charlie Brewer collects his third score of the first half and his second touchdown on the ground with a two-yard punch-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brewer rumbles in for 2nd rush TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brewer rumbles in for 2nd rush TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts is picked off by Grayland Arnold for a 71-yard return, then Charlie Brewer hits Denzel Mims for another touchdown on the proceeding play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts' pick tees up instant Baylor TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts' pick tees up instant Baylor TD

videos.description: Oklahoma scores its first touchdown of the game late in the second quarter as Jalen Hurts connects with Austin Stogner for a five-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts darts TD pass to Stogner) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts darts TD pass to Stogner

videos.description: Jalen Hurts rolls right and fires a red-zone touchdown to Austin Stogner for their second scoring connection of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts, Stogner connect again for TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts, Stogner connect again for TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts coughs up his second fumble of the game as James Lynch jars the ball loose right before Hurts reaches the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts loses ball inches before breaking plane) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts loses ball inches before breaking plane

videos.description: Jalen Hurts slings a pass out to Theo Wease, who jukes Baylor defenders and dives into the end zone for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wease shakes Baylor defenders en route to TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wease shakes Baylor defenders en route to TD

videos.description: Nik Bonitto jumps a Charlie Brewer pass on Baylor's final drive and the interception completes Oklahoma's 25-point comeback.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sooners seal comeback win with pick of Brewer) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sooners seal comeback win with pick of Brewer

videos.description: Jalen Hurts says he put the Sooners in a tough spot with multiple turnovers, but their comeback is a testament to Oklahoma's inner grit.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Hurts on comeback: Teams are remembered for November success) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Hurts on comeback: Teams are remembered for November success

videos.description: After a rocky start in the first half, Jalen Hurts leads the Sooners' 25-point comeback with four touchdowns to hand Baylor its first loss.
